<i>Note: conditions should be in a comma-delimited list with no spaces between -- eg "A,B,C,D"</i>

<p><br><br><b>Node substitutions</b>:

[{editvars}]
<i>Syntax is CONDITION|ORIGINAL -> SUBSTITUTE, where ORIGINAL and SUBSTITUTE are htmlcodes -- to substitute htmlcode "yesno_field" with "yesno_field_2" in condition A the key is "A|yesno_field" with value "yesno_field_2".</i>
